    Atom
    Interface for atoms.
    AtomImpl
    Implements Atom objects.

    Interface for TermType.BLANK terms.
    BlankImpl
    Implements Blank terms.
    ClassToRuleBodyConverter
    Helper class for transforming OWL class expressions that occur as subclasses into suitable body atoms for rules.
    ClassToRuleHeadConverter
    Helper class for transforming OWL class expressions that occur as superclasses into suitable head atoms for rules.
    ConfigureReasonerLogging
    This class exemplifies setting a log file and log level for VLog reasoner logging information (like materialisation duration, number of iterations, number of derivations).
    Conjunction
    Interface for representing conjunctions of Atoms, i.e., lists of atomic formulas that are connected with logical AND.
    ConjunctionImpl
    Simple implementation of Conjunction.
    Constant
    Interface for constants, i.e., terms of type TermType.CONSTANT.
    ConstantImpl
    Implements Constant terms.
    CsvFileDataSource
    An CsvFileDataSource stores facts in the CSV format inside a file of the extension .csv.
    DataSource
    Interfaces various types of data sources for storing facts.
    EdbIdbSeparationException
    Exception thrown when attempting to load the reasoner with a knowledge base (facts and rules) that contains predicates that are both EDB (occur in facts) and IDB (occur in rule heads).
    ExamplesUtils  
    Expressions
    This utilities class provides static methods for creating terms and formulas in vlog4j.
    FileDataSource
    A FileDataSource is an abstract implementation of a storage for fact terms in a file of some format.
    IncompatiblePredicateArityException
    Expression thrown when attempting to load the reasoner with a knowledge base that contains facts from a DataSource (added with Reasoner.addFactsFromDataSource(Predicate, DataSource)), whose arity does not correspond to the arity of the Predicate the data source was added for.
    LogLevel  
    OwlAxiomToRulesConverter
    Class for converting OWL axioms to rules.
    OwlFeatureNotSupportedException
    Exception that indicates that the translation of OWL into rules has failed due to an expressive feature of OWL that cannot be captured in rules.
    OwlOntologyToRulesAndFacts
    This example shows how vlog4j-owlapi library (class OwlToRulesConverter) can be used to transform an OWL ontology into vlog4j-core Rules and Atoms.
    OwlToRulesConversionHelper
    Utility class for helper functions that are used to convert OWL API objects to rules.
    OwlToRulesConverter
    Class for converting OWL ontologies to rules.
    Predicate

    PredicateImpl
    Implementation for Predicate.
    QueryResult
    A Query Result represents a list of terms that match the terms of the asked query.
    QueryResultIterator
    Iterates trough all answers to a query.
    RdfFileDataSource
    An RdfFileDataSource stores facts in the RDF N-Triples format inside a file of the extension .nt.
    RdfModelToAtomsConverter
    Class for converting RDF Models to Atom sets.
    Reasoner
    Interface that exposes the existential rule reasoning capabilities of VLog.
    ReasonerState
    Enum for the states a Reasoner can be in.
    ReasonerStateException
    Thrown when an operation that is invalid in current reasoner state is attempted.
    Rule
    Interface for classes representing a rule.
    RuleImpl
    Implementation for Rule.
    RuleRewriteStrategy  
    SkolemVsRestrictedChaseTermination
    This example shows non-termination of the Skolem Chase, versus termination of the Restricted Chase on the same set of rules and facts.
    SparqlQueryResultDataSource
    A SparqlQueryResultDataSource provide the results of a SPARQL query on a given web endpoint.
    Term
    Interface for terms.
    TermFilter
    A visitor that builds a set of terms of a specific type.
    TermType
    Enumeration listing the different types of terms (TermType.CONSTANT, TermType.BLANK, and TermType.VARIABLE).
    TermVisitor<T>
    A visitor for the various types of Terms in the data model.
    Variable
    Interface for variables, i.e., terms of type TermType.VARIABLE.
    VariableImpl
    Implements Variable terms.
